dataset.title: Relevés d'invertébrés sur la Nonette à Gouvieux par la méthode IBG-DCE

abstract.para: This dataset is collected as part of the process of monitoring river quality for the implementation of the Water framework directive. It describes the number of invertebrates observed in July 2010 at the station of river Nonette in Gouvieux (Picardie).
